Miscellaneous Highlights: Samuel Eto'o donated 500 tickets to students to attend the Cameroon vs Kenya match on October 11, 2024, at the Ahmadou Ahidjo Omnisport Stadium.
Others: The match between Cameroon and Kenya is part of the third round of qualifying for the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations in Morocco.
Cameroon and Kenya share the top spot in Group J with four points each.
Namibia remains at zero points after two matches.
